    <p><span style="color: #ab0634;"><strong>Actors: </strong></span><span class="actors"></span></p>
    <p><span style="color: #ab0634;"><strong>Plot: </strong></span><span class="plot"></span></p>
    <p><span style="color: #ab0634;"><strong>Rated: </strong></span><span class="rated"></span></p>
